---------
PROGRAM:-
---------
p=int(input('enter principle amount:'))
t=int(input('enter time:'))
r=int(input('enter rate of interest:'))
si=(p*t*r)/100
print('simple interest:',si)
emi=(p+si)/(12*t)
print('EMI=',emi)
-------
OUTPUT:-
--------
enter principle amount:30000
enter time:5
enter rate of interest:30
simple interest: 45000.0
EMI= 1250.0
